  "description": "Reference SoM manifest snippet for E1M-V2M101 — Alp Lab E1M-X V2N-M1 family member (Renesas RZ/V2N + DeepX M1). Two SKUs in the family (E1M-V2M101 / E1M-V2M102) differ in memory tier (32/32 vs 64/128 Gbit). Sister family E1M-X V2N (E1M-V2N101 / E1M-V2N102) is the same module without DeepX M1. Routes the standard's primary functions on most pads; alt-uses GPIO on a handful for board-level signalling.",
